        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2095005772" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6870674166422219257">This series was the first Asimov books I ever read, a long, long, long time ago, as a teenager. The first one I read (out of order) was The Robots of Dawn, and I loved it. Never before had I read such a wonderful blend of classic SF with classic mystery. The end just blew me away, and I thought it was the coolest thing I had ever read. So... this year, as an adult, I revisited these books to see if they would leave the same impression. I still absolutely loved them. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


